Kratak opis stranice:
Službena stranica Filozofskog fakulteta u Osijeku koja omogućuje studentima, nastavnom osoblju i drugim djelatnicima pristup informacijama. 
Korišteni alati i testno okruženje
•	Windows 11 OS
•	preglednik Google Chrome (149.0.7827.115)
•	rezoluciji zaslona 1920x1080
•	korišteni alat: cypress
Scope testiranja: automatizirano testiranje navigacije kroz glavni izbornik, preuzimanje rasporeda sati te pretraživanje sadržaja pomoću tražilice.

Test cases

Test Case ID: TC-001
Test Case Description: As a user, I expect to be able to download a timetable file for a specific department.
Preconditions: User is on the homepage. 
Test Steps: 
1. Open website https://www.ffos.unios.hr/ .
2. From the top menu, click on "Odsjeci i katedre".
3. Click on "Odsjek za informacijske znanosti".
4. On the page scroll down to "Raspored sati".
5. Click on "Raspored sati".
6. On the new page click on "Informatologija, Nakladništvo i Informacijske tehnologije" to download the timetable.
Expected Result: The timetable file is downloaded.
Test Result: Pass, the timetable file was downloaded successfully. 

Test Case ID: TC-002
Test Case Description: As a user, I expect the ability to search the page using the built in search bar.
Preconditions: User is on the home page. 
Test Steps: 
1. Open website https://www.ffos.unios.hr/ .
2. Click on the search field located on the top right corner of the page.
3. Type in "Upisi 2026" and click on the search icon or press enter.
Expected Result: Results containing "Upisi 2026" are listed.
Test Result: Pass, results containing "Upisi" and "2026" are shown. 
